        "comment": "25 to 50 cm of snow, and even more in some localities, has fallen. <br/> The wind was violent in some cases. On Friday the wind will be strong to storm force. The wind will transport the new snow significantly. <br/> <br/> The new snow and wind slabs are lying on the unfavourable surface of an old snowpack above the tree line. The old snowpack will be weakly bonded, especially on west, north and east facing slopes above approximately 2200 m, and on south facing slopes at elevated altitudes."
